<font color="yellow">Aku akan bernegosiasi denganmu.</font>

183
00:15:15,924 --> 00:15:18,084
<font color="yellow">Apa yang hendak kau lakukan?</font>

184
00:15:18,154 --> 00:15:19,784
<font color="yellow">Aku akan merebut...</font>

185
00:15:21,384 --> 00:15:23,354
<font color="yellow">...milik Seja asli,</font>

186
00:15:24,854 --> 00:15:25,954
<font color="yellow">segalanya.</font>

187
00:15:28,854 --> 00:15:30,384
<font color="yellow">Aku akan merebut segalanya dari dia.</font>

188
00:15:31,124 --> 00:15:32,754
<font color="yellow">Dengar yang aku katakan.</font>

189
00:15:32,754 --> 00:15:35,854
<font color="yellow">Pemilihan Ratu sebelumnya digelar oleh para pengkhianat,</font>

190
00:15:35,854 --> 00:15:37,154
<font color="yellow">sehingga tidak valid.</font>

191
00:15:37,154 --> 00:15:39,784
<font color="yellow">Sekarang, saatnya untuk menggelar pemilihan ulang.</font>

192
00:15:39,924 --> 00:15:42,854
<font color="yellow">Aku sudah memutuskan Ratuku sendiri.</font>

193
00:15:42,854 --> 00:15:44,924
<font color="yellow">Sekarang, aku akan mengumumkannya.</font>

194
00:15:45,054 --> 00:15:48,454
<font color="yellow">Anak itu, putri dari Hakim Hanseongbu,</font>

195
00:15:48,754 --> 00:15:50,554
<font color="yellow">Han Gyu Ho Eureushin,</font>

196
00:15:50,824 --> 00:15:51,854
<font color="yellow">yang akan dipulihkan kehormatannya,</font>

197
00:15:51,854 --> 00:15:54,784
<font color="yellow">Han Ga Eun, akan menjadi Ratuku.</font>

198
00:16:05,424 --> 00:16:08,954
<font color="yellow">"Jungungjeon (kediaman Ratu) telah kosong untuk waktu yang cukup lama."</font>

199
00:16:08,954 --> 00:16:11,084
<font color="yellow">"Sebab itu, aku memerlukan sosok wanita yang baik hati dan tulus..."</font>

200
00:16:11,284 --> 00:16:14,054
<font color="yellow">"...melayani Raja,"</font>

201
00:16:14,054 --> 00:16:17,924
<font color="yellow">"untuk menjadi Ratu negeri ini."</font>

202
00:16:18,324 --> 00:16:21,724
<font color="yellow">Sebab itu, aku memilih Han Ga Eun,</font>

203
00:16:21,724 --> 00:16:24,124
<font color="yellow">menjadi ibu dari rakyat negeri ini,</font>

204
00:16:24,124 --> 00:16:27,054
<font color="yellow">dan memenuhi tugas sebagai Ratu.</font>

205
00:16:34,184 --> 00:16:35,384
<font color="yellow">Dae Mok Eureushin.</font>

206
00:16:35,624 --> 00:16:37,124
<font color="yellow">Anak itu berani...</font>

207
00:16:37,124 --> 00:16:39,624
<font color="yellow">...memilih istri seenaknya.</font>

208
00:16:39,624 --> 00:16:42,684
<font color="yellow">Bahkan, dia memilih putri dari orang yang menentang Pyunsoo-hwe
di masa lalu,</font>

209
00:16:42,684 --> 00:16:44,724
<font color="yellow">dan telah dibunuh atas dosanya.</font>

210
00:16:46,054 --> 00:16:49,224
<font color="yellow">Padahal kupikir Perdana Menteri yang akan menjadi mertua Raja.</font>

211
00:16:49,284 --> 00:16:51,184
<font color="yellow">Kau pasti sangat kecewa, bukan begitu?</font>

212
00:16:51,184 --> 00:16:53,184
<font color="yellow">Wakil Perdana Menteri, kurasa kau...</font>

213
00:16:53,424 --> 00:16:56,484
<font color="yellow">..yang lebih kecewa karena mengira Raja akan memilihmu...</font>

214
00:16:57,084 --> 00:16:58,684
<font color="yellow">...sebagai ayah mertuanya.</font>

215
00:17:01,154 --> 00:17:02,954
<font color="yellow">Memilih anak itu sebagai Ratu,</font>

216
00:17:03,424 --> 00:17:06,424
<font color="yellow">akulah yang memberinya izin.</font>

217
00:17:07,854 --> 00:17:09,794
<font color="yellow">Mengapa Anda melakukannya?</font>

218
00:17:10,184 --> 00:17:12,684
<font color="yellow">Ratu semestinya berasal dari Pyunsoo-hwe.</font>

219
00:17:12,684 --> 00:17:15,924
<font color="yellow">Kau perlu memilih umpan yang tepat untuk memancing ikan!</font>

220
00:17:15,924 --> 00:17:18,854
<font color="yellow">Tidak bisa asal memakai umpan!</font>

221
00:17:21,684 --> 00:17:25,054
<font color="yellow">Ratu bisa kita ubah setiap saat.</font>

222
00:17:25,054 --> 00:17:27,554
<font color="yellow">Jangan membuat keributan atas masalah sepele begini.</font>

223
00:17:27,554 --> 00:17:28,854
<font color="yellow">Tapi, tetap saja,</font>

224
00:17:28,854 --> 00:17:31,524
<font color="yellow">pemilihan Ratu bukanlah sesuatu yang sepe--</font>

225
00:17:32,084 --> 00:17:33,254
<font color="yellow">Dae Mok Eureushin.</font>

226
00:17:49,184 --> 00:17:50,354
<font color="yellow">Tak apa.</font>

227
00:17:53,524 --> 00:17:56,524
<font color="yellow">Kepala Saudagar yang mengirim kau?</font>

228
00:17:56,554 --> 00:17:57,754
<font color="yellow">Kepala Saudagar...</font>

229
00:17:59,984 --> 00:18:01,424
<font color="yellow">..sudah meninggal.</font>

230
00:18:03,654 --> 00:18:04,754
<font color="yellow">Hwa Gun..</font>

231
00:18:06,254 --> 00:18:07,984
<font color="yellow">Kepala Saudagar... sudah meninggal?</font>

232
00:18:11,954 --> 00:18:13,584
<font color="yellow">Apa yang kudengar itu benar?</font>

233
00:18:15,154 --> 00:18:16,624
<font color="yellow">Dae Mok...</font>

234
00:18:17,454 --> 00:18:20,084
<font color="yellow">...membunuh sendiri cucunya.</font>

235
00:18:20,724 --> 00:18:21,984
<font color="yellow">Kepala Saudagar,</font>

236
00:18:23,124 --> 00:18:24,554
<font color="yellow">bagaimana aku...</font>

237
00:18:25,254 --> 00:18:27,754
<font color="yellow">...harus membayar kebaikanmu ini?</font>

238
00:18:30,184 --> 00:18:31,654
<font color="yellow">Tolong jadilah Raja.</font>

239
00:18:35,224 --> 00:18:36,724
<font color="yellow">Aghassi pasti menginginkan...</font>

240
00:18:36,724 --> 00:18:39,224
<font color="yellow">...Jeoha merebut kembali takhta Raja.</font>

241
00:18:39,754 --> 00:18:41,084
<font color="yellow">Pengorbanan Aghassi,</font>

242
00:18:43,354 --> 00:18:44,984
<font color="yellow">tolong jangan menyia-nyiakan itu.</font>

243
00:18:48,524 --> 00:18:52,224
<font color="yellow">Bukan orang lain, justru Daepyunsoo sendiri.</font>

244
00:18:52,454 --> 00:18:54,384
<font color="yellow">Bagamana bisa dia membakar ladang poppi?</font>

245
00:18:54,524 --> 00:18:56,454
<font color="yellow">Dia itu cucumu, Dae Mok!</font>

246
00:18:56,554 --> 00:18:58,754
<font color="yellow">Untuk membayar dosanya itu,</font>

247
00:18:59,024 --> 00:19:00,584
<font color="yellow">aku sudah menghabisinya.</font>

248
00:19:00,584 --> 00:19:04,294
<font color="yellow">Apakah lantas semuanya beres hanya dengan membunuhnya?</font>

249
00:19:04,454 --> 00:19:08,024
<font color="yellow">Pyunsoo-hwe kita kehilangan ladang poppi yang berharga.</font>

250
00:19:08,354 --> 00:19:10,454
<font color="yellow">Apa rencanamu sekarang?</font>

251
00:19:10,524 --> 00:19:11,924
<font color="yellow">Aku berencana...</font>

252
00:19:14,524 --> 00:19:18,654
<font color="yellow">...menggunakan kesempatan ini untuk mengubah Pyunsoo-hwe.</font>

253
00:19:18,724 --> 00:19:20,454
<font color="yellow">Aku akan membuat daftar.</font>

254
00:19:21,654 --> 00:19:23,854
<font color="yellow">Siapapun yang menentang Pyunsoo-hwe,</font>

255
00:19:23,854 --> 00:19:25,824
<font color="yellow">harus mati, tanpa ampun.</font>

256
00:19:25,824 --> 00:19:28,224
<font color="yellow">Bila menolak setia kepada Pyunsoo-hwe,</font>

257
00:19:28,854 --> 00:19:30,254
<font color="yellow">mereka akan dihabisi.</font>

258
00:19:30,554 --> 00:19:32,454
<font color="yellow">Aku sudah memberi contoh nyata (dengan kematian Hwa Gun),</font>

259
00:19:32,854 --> 00:19:35,324
<font color="yellow">jadi apapun itu, akan menjadi yang terbaik.</font>

260
00:19:39,684 --> 00:19:40,924
<font color="yellow">Ini apa?</font>

261
00:19:41,654 --> 00:19:43,054
<font color="yellow">Daftar nama.</font>

262
00:19:43,654 --> 00:19:46,984
<font color="yellow">Ini adalah salinan daftar asli yang saya buat diam-diam.</font>

263
00:19:49,854 --> 00:19:53,524
<font color="yellow">Kebakaran yang dibuat Aghassi telah membumihanguskan ladang poppi.</font>

264
00:19:53,524 --> 00:19:56,754
<font color="yellow">Sekarang, tidak ada lagi bunga poppi
maupun pil yang tersisa.</font>

265
00:19:56,754 --> 00:19:57,984
<font color="yellow">Dae Mok...</font>

266
00:19:58,324 --> 00:20:01,184
<font color="yellow">...pasti berencana membiarkan mereka yang tidak setia mati,</font>

267
00:20:01,184 --> 00:20:02,424
<font color="yellow">dan hanya yang setia...</font>

268
00:20:03,954 --> 00:20:06,154
<font color="yellow">...akan diberikan penawarnya.</font>

269
00:20:09,684 --> 00:20:10,924
<font color="yellow">Sudah kuduga.</font>

270
00:20:11,654 --> 00:20:13,294
<font color="yellow">Orang-orangnya Daebi Mama.</font>

271
00:20:13,954 --> 00:20:15,684
<font color="yellow">"Wakil Perdana Menteri".</font>

272
00:20:16,954 --> 00:20:18,024
<font color="yellow">Bukankah...</font>

273
00:20:18,794 --> 00:20:20,024
<font color="yellow">...dia orangnya Dae Mok?</font>

274
00:20:20,024 --> 00:20:21,524
<font color="yellow">Tidak tersisa banyak penawar.</font>

275
00:20:21,524 --> 00:20:24,554
<font color="yellow">Sekalipun anggota Pyunsoo-hwe,
tidak lantas akan diselamatkan.</font>

276
00:20:24,954 --> 00:20:26,184
<font color="yellow">Kalau begitu,</font>

277
00:20:26,954 --> 00:20:29,724
<font color="yellow">berapa jumlah pejabat pemerintahan yang akan mati...</font>

278
00:20:30,324 --> 00:20:31,824
<font color="yellow">...akibat kurangnya jumlah penawar?</font>

279
00:20:31,954 --> 00:20:35,724
<font color="yellow">Saya dengar, sekitar 75 orang akan mati.</font>

280
00:20:54,084 --> 00:20:55,624
<font color="yellow">Orang-orang...</font>

281
00:20:56,954 --> 00:21:00,254
<font color="yellow">Kumpulkan mereka semua.
Aku ingin menyampaikan sesuatu...</font>

282
00:21:02,754 --> 00:21:04,424
<font color="yellow">...pada mereka.</font>

283
00:21:09,824 --> 00:21:12,054
<font color="yellow">"Aku adalah putra seorang pengkhianat,"</font>

284
00:21:13,224 --> 00:21:15,854
<font color="yellow">"tapi aku masih layak menjadi Raja?"</font>

285
00:21:17,294 --> 00:21:19,824
<font color="yellow">Aku sudah berpikir keras akan hal itu, dan...</font>

286
00:21:21,794 --> 00:21:25,024
<font color="yellow">aku sudah membuat keputusan.</font>

287
00:21:28,524 --> 00:21:31,984
<font color="yellow">Mendiang Raja memang bekerja sama dengan Pyunsoo-hwe
untuk merebut takhta, namun...</font>

288
00:21:31,984 --> 00:21:33,154
<font color="yellow">...aku...</font>

289
00:21:35,124 --> 00:21:37,354
<font color="yellow">...akan melenyapkan Pyunsoo-hwe,</font>

290
00:21:38,484 --> 00:21:40,024
<font color="yellow">dan menjadi Raja sesungguhnya.</font>

291
00:21:53,784 --> 00:21:57,184
<font color="yellow">Bila kita tidak mendapatkan penawarnya 12 hari mulai sekarang,</font>

292
00:21:57,184 --> 00:22:00,024
<font color="yellow">ketujuh puluh lima pejabat pemerintahan dalam daftar ini,</font>

293
00:22:01,154 --> 00:22:02,754
<font color="yellow">akan kehilangan nyawa mereka.</font>

294
00:22:05,284 --> 00:22:07,084
<font color="yellow">Mereka mungkin anggota Pyunsoo-hwe,</font>

295
00:22:07,224 --> 00:22:08,854
<font color="yellow">tapi mereka tetaplah rakyatku.</font>

296
00:22:09,954 --> 00:22:12,484
<font color="yellow">Bila aku mengabaikan nyawa rakyatku,</font>

297
00:22:12,484 --> 00:22:14,784
<font color="yellow">bagaimana bisa aku menyebut diriku Raja?</font>

298
00:22:17,624 --> 00:22:18,624
<font color="yellow">Dan juga,</font>

299
00:22:19,484 --> 00:22:20,554
<font color="yellow">sekarang aku...</font>

300
00:22:21,424 --> 00:22:23,124
<font color="yellow">...akan merebut kembali takhta Raja.</font>

301
00:22:24,854 --> 00:22:27,624
<font color="yellow">Aku tidak akan ragu lagi.</font>

302
00:22:28,854 --> 00:22:30,254
<font color="yellow">Aku akan merebut takhta Raja,</font>

303
00:22:30,354 --> 00:22:33,024
<font color="yellow">membuat penawarnya,  dan menyelamatkan rakyatku.</font>

304
00:22:33,254 --> 00:22:34,954
<font color="yellow">Atas manipulasi terhadap Kerajaan selama ini,</font>

305
00:22:34,954 --> 00:22:37,484
<font color="yellow">aku akan menghukum Dae Mok dan juga Pyunsoo-hwe.</font>

306
00:22:40,454 --> 00:22:41,454
<font color="yellow">Maukah...</font>

307
00:22:42,984 --> 00:22:44,024
<font color="yellow">...kalian semua...</font>

308
00:22:45,624 --> 00:22:47,284
<font color="yellow">...membantuku mewujudkannya?</font>

309
00:23:01,484 --> 00:23:02,854
<font color="yellow">Jusang Cheonha.</font>

310
00:23:04,724 --> 00:23:06,954
<font color="yellow">Hamba akan melaksanakan titah Baginda.</font>

